  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've been hired as the primary elevator operator of the newly constructed high-capacity space hotel. Your job is to move characters up and down between floors as efficiently as possible in order to keep your phone's battery high and healthy. If the battery reaches zero, <strong>you're fired</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This hotel is certainly pretty popular, after all...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short game, 1-3 hours</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features a 4 day work week!!!!!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A diverse cast of unique characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spacey EDM  soundtrack</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've been hired as the primary elevator operator of the newly constructed high-capacity space hotel. Your job is to move characters up and down between floors as efficiently as possible in order to keep your phone's battery high and healthy. If the battery reaches zero, <strong>you're fired</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This hotel is certainly pretty popular, after all...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short game, 1-3 hours</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features a 4 day work week!!!!!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A diverse cast of unique characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spacey EDM  soundtrack</p></li></ul>",
